=== 游戏机 ===

* [[Coleco|Coleco]]发行了一系列新[[Coleco_Telstar|Telstar]]游戏机型号：Telstar Alpha、Telstar Colormatic、Telstar Regent、Telstar Ranger、Telstar Galaxy和Telstar Combat。大多系统和原型号差别不大，如采用新[[游戏控制器|控制器]]类型（如Ranger的[[光线枪|光线枪]]，Galaxy的[[游戏摇杆|摇杆]]）<ref name="mhvg">{{cite web | author=Goldberg, Martin | year=2003 | title=Museum of Home Video Gaming | url=http://www.classicgaming.com/gamingmuseum/museum.html | accessdate=18 February 2006 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060211022344/http://www.classicgaming.com/gamingmuseum/museum.html | archivedate=2006-02-11 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
* [[任天堂|任天堂]]发行了专用游戏机[[Color_TV-Game|Color TV-Game 6]]，收录6款《轻网球》（《[[乓|乓]]》的仿制品）变种。系统硬件部分大多由任天堂合作伙伴[[三菱|三菱]]生产<ref name="colortvgame">{{cite web | title=Color TV Game 6 | url=http://www.nindb.net/game/color-tv-game-6.html | work=[http://www.nindb.net/ NinDB] | accessdate=18 February 2006 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5j5HJvJbk?url=http://www.nindb.net/color-tv-game-6.html | archivedate=2009-08-17 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
* [[巴利技术|巴利技术]]通过[[邮购|邮购]]零售商JS&A National Sales Group，发行了[[Astrocade|巴利家庭图书馆电脑]]（Astrocade）。但因系统生产延期，直到[[1978年电子游戏界|次年]]才真正出货<ref name="bally">{{cite web | author=Squire, Lance F. | year=2005 | title=The Bally/Astrocade FAQ version h2.8 | url=http://www.alteeve.com/~lance/Ballyfaq.html | work=[http://www.alteeve.com/~lance/ Lance F. Squire Homepage] | accessdate=19 February 2006 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060207091032/http://www.alteeve.com/~lance/Ballyfaq.html | archivedate=2006-02-07 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。
* [[RCA|RCA]]公司在一月发行游戏机[[RCA_Studio_II|Studio II]]<ref name="studioII">{{cite web | author=Miller, Michael | year=2005 | title=A History of Home Video Game Consoles > First Generation: 1972–1977 | url=http://www.informit.com/articles/article.aspx?p=378141 | work=[[InformIT|InformIT]] | accessdate=18 February 2006 | archive-date=2007-12-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071226012027/http://www.informit.com/articles/article.aspx?p=378141 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* 9月11日，雅达利发行[[雅达利2600|视频电脑系统]]（Video Computer System，簡稱VCS，后称雅达利2600），有9款[[首发游戏|首发游戏]]随之推出<ref name="avcs">{{cite web| year=2006| title=Atari 2600 History| url=http://www.atariage.com/2600/history.html| work=[http://www.atariage.com/ AtariAge]| accessdate=18 February 2006| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060219101823/http://www.atariage.com/2600/history.html| archivedate=2006-02-19| deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 游戏 ===

* [[Cinematronics|Cinematronics]]在[[矢量图形|矢量图形]]街机上发行了[[拉里·罗森塔尔|拉里·罗森塔尔]]的《[[Space_Wars|Space Wars]]》<ref name="spacewars">{{cite web | author=Hunter, William | year=2005 | title=Player 2 Stage 1: The Coin Eaters | url=http://www.thedoteaters.com/p2_stage1.php | work=[http://www.thedoteaters.com/ The Dot Eaters] | accessdate=18 February 2006 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071231000817/http://www.thedoteaters.com/p2_stage1.php | archive-date=2007-12-31 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
* [[蒂姆·安德森|蒂姆·安德森]]、[[马克·布莱克|马克·布莱克]]、[[布鲁克·丹尼尔斯|布鲁克·丹尼尔斯]]和[[戴夫·列柏龄|戴夫·列柏龄]]，后来[[Infocom|Infocom]]的创办人，在[[麻省理工学院|麻省理工学院]][[Project_MAC|计算机科学实验室]]的[[PDP-10|PDP-10]]上开发了第一版《[[魔域|魔域]]》<ref name="zork">{{cite web | title=History of Infocom | url=http://www.infocom-if.org/company/company.html | work=[http://www.infocom-if.org/ Infocom – The Master Storytellers] | accessdate=18 February 2006 | archive-date=2020-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226044026/http://www.infocom-if.org/company/company.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
* [[克尔顿·芬灵|克尔顿·芬灵]]在[[弗吉尼亚大学|弗吉尼亚大学]]读[[哲學博士|博]]期间，开始开发文字空战游戏《[[Air_(1977年游戏)|Air]]》。游戏成为首款[[大型多人在线游戏|大型多人在线游戏]]——1987年《[[Air_Warrior|Air Warrior]]》——的早期先驱<ref name="air">{{cite web | author=Koster, Raph | year=2002 | title=Online World Timeline | url=http://www.raphkoster.com/gaming/mudtimeline.shtml | work=[http://www.raphkoster.com/ Raph Koster's Website] | accessdate=18 February 2006 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060214010936/http://www.raphkoster.com/gaming/mudtimeline.shtml | archivedate=2006-02-14 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。

